For the down spokes:
=============================================
To calculate the srep area and volume entropy:
correspondence('/NIRAL/work/ltu/WorkSpace/data_pablo/Pablo2/lib/vtksrep/Correspondence/output_feature/srepareavolume_down/',3);

To calculate the srep horizonal edges entropy:
correspondence('/NIRAL/work/ltu/WorkSpace/data_pablo/Pablo2/lib/vtksrep/Correspondence/output_feature/srephorizonal_down/',2);

To calculate the srep vertical edges entropy:
correspondence('/NIRAL/work/ltu/WorkSpace/data_pablo/Pablo2/lib/vtksrep/Correspondence/output_feature/srepvertical_down/',2);






